1359.name: Nicro 92
1359.Applications: Cladding applications to resist extreme high temperatures and thermal shocks in extreme corrosive invironments.
1359.Suitable_For: Joining Inconel and Incoloy alloys to stainless steels, carbon steels, Monel alloys, joining Monel alloys and Nickel 200 to stainless steels and joining stainless steels to carbon steels. This filler metal can also be used for welding Nickel steels. Excelent for cladding valves and pistons at high working temperature engines.
